       <div class="col-md-6 rounded-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center flex-column left-box" style="background: #103cbe;">
           <p class="text-white fs-2" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-weight: 600;">Tech Blog</p>
           <small class="text-white text-wrap text-center" style="width: 17rem;font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;">WELCOME TO TECH BLOG</small>
       </div> 
